entries.name: LuxorTempleFirstCourtNight
entries.description: This CAVEcam was shot in the Luxor Temple showing the First Court of Ramesses II and the 14th Century Mosque of Abu al-Haggag, at night.  See: http://www.calit2.net/newsroom/rss.php?id=1862 and http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Luxor_Temple

entries.name: LuxorMedinetHabuHypostyle
entries.description:
This CAVEcam was shot in the Temple of Ramesses III at Medinet Habu. This is outside of the columns CAVEcam shot and the Royal Treasure Halls.
See: http://www.calit2.net/newsroom/rss.php?id=1862
and http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Medinet_Habu_(temple)
